{"tid":2030778,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"第18條凶間 國安惡法 劍指立會","createTime":"2020-05-23T04:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T05:14:01.000Z","uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b0c4fe69223de867433e808d584d1a2a896ea237","tid":2030778,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:00:01.000Z","msg":"【法政奄列】 第18條凶間（劉偉聰）<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200522/SY57OE7A3LZO2ZQD3CBGYE2EKI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200522%2FSY57OE7A3LZO2ZQD3CBGYE2EKI%2F&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CADpGYGFnKQRHckm7FIFNPY%3D&h=c4d40a36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200522%2FSY57OE7A3LZO2ZQD3CBGYE2EKI%2F&h=2acc4bf2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200522/SY57OE7A3LZO2ZQD3CBGYE2EKI/</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;又或大人先生們更懂得瞻前顧後，早早籌謀，早早立法，早早以國家安全或勾結外國勢力之名，將立法會未來民主派候選人捉個一乾二淨，睇你點死！&quot;<br />\n<br />\n其實惡法並無明確實施時間，亦可能只係隨意門用嚟恐嚇香港人係立會選舉歸邊。要反制就要有共識，例如<br />\n一份明確國際制裁名單<br />\n條例一旦實施，每個人會將最少幾多資產轉走<br />\n. . ."},{"pid":"e9cfd650ea9a0a8a5b314480dd1c754dd167806d","tid":2030778,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:01:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"910e228630d3a2dcf7ef6c22eb57adec7714eec8","tid":2030778,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:03:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bab47e3e00847d86f70ab1018a9e0f5df5e01d28","tid":2030778,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:06:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"facc084c7de6c3b7ae94275ec5aa201af577c2e7","tid":2030778,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:08:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8c4c97853ce6b0d580a536abfabeed62797ae81f","tid":2030778,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:10:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"256dabb48f30d53a4637ec82e3515d82edfcd889","tid":2030778,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:12:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cf794ff2a6cf0f993a33efa52e4ff4be628497c4","tid":2030778,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:17:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2382d3d0e69c003729e98cc6fe23b2d4241515f1","tid":2030778,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:19:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2ff7933a6e98690ecd30793b4a45fc8236f03d2e","tid":2030778,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:14:01.000Z","msg":"美國緊盯 富豪巧合缺席<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200523/GMFNU7AIWXSKQH3YOJ2YWXAVNQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200523%2FGMFNU7AIWXSKQH3YOJ2YWXAVNQ%2F&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CADpGYGFnKQRHckm7FIFNPY%3D&h=cd5a7aa5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200523%2FGMFNU7AIWXSKQH3YOJ2YWXAVNQ%2F&h=2d2b3837\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200523/GMFNU7AIWXSKQH3YOJ2YWXAVNQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港版「國安法」突然被納入人大會議議程，據往績，一般都會獲人大代表通過。然而，美國去年11月落實《香港人權與民主法案》等，香港富豪若有份在會議中投票通過，或成美國日後制裁的話柄。巧合地，長和系現任掌舵人李澤鉅及騰訊創辦人馬化騰，都因身體問題而沒有出席人大會議。即使有任何困難決定，都毋須親手投票通過。<br />\n<br />\n李澤鉅馬化騰因病請假<br />\n<br />\n李澤鉅上周在多場長和系股東會露面，惟會上多次咳嗽，公司發言人亦確認李患上感冒。後來，長和再補充，李澤鉅因為發燒，近日已沒有上班，亦未能登機前往北京出席人大會議等。此外，騰訊主席馬化騰較早前亦獲確認，因身體原因向兩會請假。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，即使是建制派也有人缺席會議，包括工聯會鄭耀棠及「建制派班長」廖長江。"}]}